article_id:2112,category_name:Events,title_name:A New Quest, Trials of the Mighty, Is Coming!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/e3feafd9615f9e914c5a00e4639ba0a9.png,message:<div>A new series of quests, Trials of the Mighty, debuts on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1617775200"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/e3feafd9615f9e914c5a00e4639ba0a9.png"></div><div>In Trials of the Mighty, you&#39;ll be challenged to take on various bosses with a team of one or more predetermined elements and weapon types. Clear these quests to earn rewards like materials for unlocking the mana spirals of certain adventurers (called &quot;convictions&quot; and &quot;devotions&quot; that are that unique to each adventurer) from the daily bonus.</div><div><br></div><hr><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/4c7900585c895e13f7c3b28c17c36cf1.png"></div><div>Suggested might for Thor&#39;s Trial: Standard (Light): 15,000</div><div>Suggested might for Thor&#39;s Trial: Expert (Light): 20,000</div><div>Suggested might for Thor&#39;s Trial: Master (Light): 38,000</div><div><br></div><div>■Quest Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1617775200"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1618379999"></span></div><div><br></div><div>■Eligible Element and Weapon Types</div><div>Shadow, Sword/Wand/Staff</div><div><br></div><div>■Eligible Convictions and Devotions</div><div>Gala Prince&#39;s</div><div><br></div><hr><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/f2e39c74edf05dc1236321f62524aa50.png"></div><div><br></div><div>Suggested might for Poseidon&#39;s Trial: Standard (Water): 15,000</div><div>Suggested might for Poseidon&#39;s Trial: Expert (Water): 20,000</div><div>Suggested might for Poseidon&#39;s Trial: Master (Water): 38,000</div><div><br></div><div>■Quest Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1618380000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1618984799"></span></div><div><br></div><div>■Eligible Element and Weapon Types</div><div>Wind, Dagger/Wand/Staff</div><div><br></div><div>■Eligible Convictions and Devotions</div><div>Gala Elisanne&#39;s</div><div><br></div><hr><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/234ccdfc6b52bd7382ba733512802478.png"></div><div><br></div><div>Suggested might for Zephyr&#39;s Trial: Standard (Wind): 15,000</div><div>Suggested might for Zephyr&#39;s Trial: Expert (Wind); 20,000</div><div>Suggested might for Zephyr&#39;s Trial: Master (Wind): 38,000</div><div><br></div><div>■Quest Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1618984800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1619589599"></span></div><div><br></div><div>■Eligible Element and Weapon Types</div><div>Flame, Axe/Lance/Staff</div><div><br></div><div>■Eligible Convictions and Devotions</div><div>Gala Ranzal&#39;s</div><div><br></div><hr><div><br></div><div>■Daily Bonus</div><div>Materials for unlocking the mana spirals of certain adventurers (called &quot;convictions&quot; and &quot;devotions&quot; that are that unique to each adventurer) are available from the daily bonus. Rewards from the daily bonus are obtained automatically when earned.</div><div><br></div><div>Note that the daily bonus for Trials of the Mighty differs from the traditional daily bonus in that players may stock multiple unearned bonuses. This stock grows incrementally by one every day at 6:00 AM (up to a maximum of three).</div><div><br></div><div>Note: Players must have completed up to Chapter 10 / 6-3 (Normal) of the main campaign to participate.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1617602400,update_time1617587844